OL,6,FA community drop-in event has been
OL,7,Fopened to the public to restore and re-
OL,8,Fpurpose the building for new uses
OL,9,Fincluding a world-class hotel and
OL,10,Fvenue, space for local businesses and
OL,11,Fcommunity uses, new homes and a new,
OL,12,Fmore sustainable and cost-efficient
OL,13,Fbuilding for employees.
OL,15,FDerbyshire County Council's deputy
OL,16,Fcouncil leader, Councillor Simon
OL,17,FSpencer described the plans as
OL,18,F'phenomenal' but has said public money
