OL,4,Cover 'phenomenal' development plans
OL,6,FCommunity drop-in events are open
OL,7,Ftoday and tomorrow (February 7-8).
OL,8,FResidents will be able to view the
OL,9,Fplans and leave comments.
OL,11,FIn a bid to turn Derbyshire County
OL,12,FCouncil's vision into a reality they
OL,13,Fhave worked with local stakeholders
OL,14,Fsince 2022. The council has also
OL,15,Freceived interest from developers,
OL,16,Fhotel operators and investors in being
OL,17,Finvolved with the project.
