OL,3,CDerbyshire town cautiously optimistic
OL,4,Cover 'phenomenal' development plans
OL,6,FDeputy Council Leader, Councillor
OL,7,FSimon Spencer, said: "We have a unique
OL,8,Fopportunity to restore this beautiful
OL,9,Flocal landmark and return it to its
OL,10,Foriginal purpose as a hotel, and by
OL,11,Fdoing so, support our community by
OL,12,Fgrowing the local economy, delivering
OL,13,Fnew homes and generating jobs.
OL,15,F"We want to turn County Hall back to
OL,16,FSmedley's Hydro, which was the
OL,17,Foriginal name of the buildings.
